   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h2>
<p>To start a new email interaction with a customer (not as a reply)</p>
<ol>
 <li>
  <p>Ensure the customer session is active.</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click the <strong>Email</strong> icon located in the top-right toolbar.</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Compose your message, add recipient(s), and enter a subject line.</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Click <strong>Send Email</strong> to initiate the outbound communication.</p>
 </li>
</ol>
<div data-component="panel" role="note" data-appearance="info">
 <div class="panel-content">
  <p>This option is only available for customers with an active session.</p>
 </div>
</div>
<p>For more details, visit this <a href="/cx-knowledgebase/latest/email#Compose-a-New-Outbound-Email-to-an-existing-Customer" data-scope="internal">page</a>.</p>
